{"tid":1185750,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"國指午市跌64點、收市跌89點　重現7年前A股離奇巧合","createTime":"2019-06-04T12:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T18:06:54.000Z","uid":56999,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbd1c3d7d278a1ebdee04041dcc61b0e4230edf","tid":1185750,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/336683/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81-%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%88%E5%B8%82%E8%B7%8C64%E9%BB%9E-%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E8%B7%8C89%E9%BB%9E-%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE7%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8Da%E8%82%A1%E9%9B%A2%E5%A5%87%E5%B7%A7%E5%90%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F336683%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258D%2581-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%25B7%258C64%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%25B7%258C89%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%258F%25BE7%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258Da%25E8%2582%25A1%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A5%2587%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E5%2590%2588&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cgp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=04ba3e83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/336683/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81-%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%88%E5%B8%82%E8%B7%8C64%E9%BB%9E-%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E8%B7%8C89%E9%BB%9E-%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE7%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8Da%E8%82%A1%E9%9B%A2%E5%A5%87%E5%B7%A7%E5%90%88</a><br />\n<br />\n六四事件今日（4日）踏入30周年，本港金融市場驚現「六四密碼」，恒指半日報26804點，跌89點；國指則報10,366點，跌64點，恰巧地出現「89」及「64」兩組數字。<br />\n<br />\n而港股午後跌幅稍為放大，恒指最終收報26761點，下跌132點，但國指收報10341點，下跌89點，出現午市跌64點、收市跌89點的巧合。<br />\n<br />\n在六四當天，金融市場出現這樣離奇的巧合，其實在7年前的內地A股市場亦出現過，2012年6月4日，當時正為六四事件23周年，上證指數在開市及收市時，數字都曾涵蓋「89」、「64」及「23」，連最後一筆交易也是「64」手。"},{"pid":"4e87b64510c40077a695d58d19c5c106549cf8fd","tid":1185750,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:38: